<br>
One of the most important points of being a mage is POSITIONING. Stay the hell away from the front rank keep the pet parked well away from aggro, and earth boot it if it goes loco.<br>
<br>
Actually TT are one of the BEST mobs to use pets on. Who cares if they dispel BO3? And their dispel knocks of mezzes anyway.<br>
You want to STUN them and nuke the HELL out of them to kill fast.<br>
<br>
Redorious<br>
